同啲泰國藥膏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b6a1c6d50c43e2b8892187a30cc96069141f8d","tid":155012,"uid":42881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:43:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲想問下如果藥膏類呢？<br />\n我想買啲喜療疤 同啲泰國藥膏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongairport.com/chi/passenger/departure/all/airport-security-faq.html#new_q1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongairport.com%2Fchi%2Fpassenger%2Fdeparture%2Fall%2Fairport-security-faq.html%23new_q1&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6b7eebd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongairport.com/chi/passenger/departure/all/airport-security-faq.html#new_q1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n液體、凝膠及噴霧類物品<br />\n問1.\t液體、凝膠及噴霧類物品是指甚麼物品?<br />\n<br />\n液體、凝膠及噴霧類物品包括：<br />\n飲料，例如水、湯、糖漿、果醬、燉煮的食物、醬汁和膏狀的食物；<br />\n在醬汁中或含有液體的食物；<br />\n乳霜、潤膚液、潤膚油、香水、化妝品，例如睫毛液、唇彩、潤唇膏；<br />\n噴劑和壓縮容器，例如刮毛泡沫及香體噴霧；<br />\n膏狀物品，例如牙膏；<br />\n凝膠，例如髮膠和沐浴露；<br />\n液體與固體之混合物 ；<br />\n在室溫下稠度類似的任何其他物品 。"}]}